04:50.874 --> 04:52.334
The fuck does that mean?

04:52.417 --> 04:54.294
- We should get out of here soon.

04:54.378 --> 04:56.672
- No, we shouldn't.
I know there's some stuff in here

04:56.755 --> 04:59.007
that he don't want us to see.
Just got to look for it.

05:00.300 --> 05:03.720
Probably got one of them, like,
secret compartments somewhere.

05:03.804 --> 05:05.347
Got it.

05:05.430 --> 05:07.224
Bingo.

05:07.307 --> 05:08.600
- Holy shit.

05:13.438 --> 05:15.357
- Here.
I got another lock for you to pick.

05:15.440 --> 05:16.817
- What do you think's in there?
- I don't know.

05:16.900 --> 05:18.902
Some shit that he don't want
nobody to find.

05:21.446 --> 05:22.739
Shit.

05:31.582 --> 05:33.208
- I'll get your ass.

05:57.065 --> 05:58.358
Oh.

05:58.442 --> 06:00.527
Isn't this interesting?

06:02.237 --> 06:05.782
Well, I know that you're both
pretending to be asleep.

06:05.866 --> 06:08.410
And that's fine. It's probably the best

06:08.493 --> 06:10.787
acting that either of you will ever do

06:10.871 --> 06:12.206
in your entire lives.

06:12.289 --> 06:14.791
Especially you, Agent Hart.

06:14.875 --> 06:17.753
But if I find out that either of you

06:17.836 --> 06:20.005
left this bunk without my permission,

06:20.088 --> 06:22.299
you'll regret the day
you ever stepped into

06:22.382 --> 06:24.885
Ron Wilcox's Action Star School.

06:33.393 --> 06:36.688
If you weren't fake sleeping,
you would have woken up.

06:59.211 --> 07:01.255
- Holy shit. That was too close.

07:01.338 --> 07:02.506
